NPC.ArthurRedman: Hi, how are you sir.
[if {global.PillarPaint} == `Green`]
    NPC.ArthurRedman: Ugh, you agreed to paint it green.
[elseif {global.PillarPaint} == `Red`]
    NPC.ArthurRedman: I like the red pillar, it shines bright under sky.
    [goto end]
[endif]
NPC.ArthurRedman: Would you paint this pillar red for me?
* Sure 
  [event Event.Paint.Red]
  [set global.PillarPaint `Red`]
  NPC.ArthurRedman: Thanks have a lovely day!
* No, Sorry.

